HEADWORD: Acropetal
<hw>A*crop"e*tal</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'a`kros</grk> summit + L. <ets>petere</ets> to seek.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Developing from below towards the apex, or from
the circumference towards the center; centripetal; -- said of certain
inflorescence.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Acrophony</ent>⟦br⟧
